lead_paragraph: Two sides who could be forgiven for casting half an eye on their forthcoming FA Cup semi-final dates fought out a draw on Saturday -- but Romelu Lukaku could easily have won it for Everton near the death.

headline.print_headline: Lukaku Misses Chances to Snatch the Points for Everton
